export const HTML = "<!-- COVER -->\n<div class=\"cover section\" id=\"cover\">\n  <div class=\"cover-badge\">DROS-FEP-2026-001 \u00b7 Field Execution Plan</div>\n  <h1 class=\"cover-title\">Field Execution<br>Plan</h1>\n  <p class=\"cover-subtitle\">Comprehensive operations playbook \u2014 organizational structure, crew assignments, weekly schedules, machinery deployment, standard operating procedures, and zone-by-zone tactical work plans for a 100-hectare rehabilitation project.</p>\n  <div class=\"cover-meta\">\n    <div class=\"cm-col\">\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Plan ID</div><div class=\"cm-val mono\">DROS-FEP-2026-001</div></div>\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Linked plan</div><div class=\"cm-val mono\">DROS-RPL-2026-001</div></div>\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Parcel</div><div class=\"cm-val\">[Parcel Name]</div></div>\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Total area</div><div class=\"cm-val\">100 hectares \u00b7 4 zones</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cm-col\">\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Duration</div><div class=\"cm-val\">24 months</div></div>\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Crew strength</div><div class=\"cm-val\">18 personnel (peak)</div></div>\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">SOPs</div><div class=\"cm-val\">7 core procedures</div></div>\n      <div class=\"cm-row\"><div class=\"cm-key\">Generated</div><div class=\"cm-val\">June 2026</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- KPI -->\n<div class=\"kpi-strip\">\n  <div class=\"kpi blue\"><div class=\"kpi-label\">Crew strength</div><div class=\"kpi-value\" style=\"color:var(--blue)\">18</div><div class=\"kpi-unit\">Peak personnel \u00b7 4 crews</div></div>\n  <div class=\"kpi amber\"><div class=\"kpi-label\">Zones</div><div class=\"kpi-value\" style=\"color:var(--amber)\">4</div><div class=\"kpi-unit\">Zone A 62% \u00b7 B 24% \u00b7 C 10% \u00b7 D 4%</div></div>\n  <div class=\"kpi green\"><div class=\"kpi-label\">SOPs</div><div class=\"kpi-value\" style=\"color:var(--green)\">7</div><div class=\"kpi-unit\">Documented procedures</div></div>\n  <div class=\"kpi teal\"><div class=\"kpi-label\">Machinery</div><div class=\"kpi-value\" style=\"color:var(--teal)\">12</div><div class=\"kpi-unit\">Equipment units deployed</div></div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 01. ORGANIZATION -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"org\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--ink);color:#fff\">&#x1F465;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 01</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Organizational Structure</h2></div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"section-desc\">The field operation is led by a Project Lead with three section leads (Soil &amp; Amendments, Planting &amp; Biology, Monitoring &amp; QA) each managing dedicated crews. Total peak crew strength is 18 personnel across all four operational crews.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"org-tree\">\n    <div class=\"org-level\">\n      <div class=\"org-node lead\"><div class=\"org-role\">Tier 1</div><div class=\"org-name\">Project Lead</div><div class=\"org-count\">1 person \u00b7 24 mo</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"org-level org-level-multi\">\n      <div class=\"org-node section\"><div class=\"org-role\">Tier 2</div><div class=\"org-name\">Field Ops Manager</div><div class=\"org-count\">1 person \u00b7 24 mo</div></div>\n      <div class=\"org-node section\"><div class=\"org-role\">Tier 2</div><div class=\"org-name\">Soil Scientist</div><div class=\"org-count\">0.5 FTE \u00b7 12 mo</div></div>\n      <div class=\"org-node section\"><div class=\"org-role\">Tier 2</div><div class=\"org-name\">HSE Officer</div><div class=\"org-count\">1 person \u00b7 24 mo</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"org-level org-level-multi\">\n      <div class=\"org-node crew\"><div class=\"org-role\">Crew Alpha</div><div class=\"org-name\">Soil Prep</div><div class=\"org-count\">6 \u00b7 weeks 1\u201310</div></div>\n      <div class=\"org-node crew\"><div class=\"org-role\">Crew Beta</div><div class=\"org-name\">Amendments</div><div class=\"org-count\">5 \u00b7 weeks 9\u201316</div></div>\n      <div class=\"org-node crew\"><div class=\"org-role\">Crew Gamma</div><div class=\"org-name\">Planting</div><div class=\"org-count\">10 \u00b7 weeks 20\u201332</div></div>\n      <div class=\"org-node crew\"><div class=\"org-role\">Crew Delta</div><div class=\"org-name\">Monitoring</div><div class=\"org-count\">3 \u00b7 mo 8\u201324</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <table class=\"dtable\">\n    <thead><tr><th>Role</th><th>Responsibility</th><th>Duration</th><th class=\"center\">FTE</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Project Lead</td><td>Overall accountability \u00b7 client interface \u00b7 gate sign-off</td><td class=\"val\">24 months</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Field Ops Manager</td><td>Daily site management \u00b7 crew coordination \u00b7 logistics</td><td class=\"val\">24 months</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-ok\"><td class=\"param\">Soil Scientist</td><td>Sample collection \u00b7 field testing \u00b7 amendment dosing decisions</td><td class=\"val\">12 months</td><td class=\"center val\">0.5</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-warn\"><td class=\"param\">HSE Officer</td><td>Daily safety briefings \u00b7 incident response \u00b7 PPE compliance</td><td class=\"val\">24 months</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Crew Alpha Lead</td><td>Earthworks \u00b7 fencing \u00b7 gypsum \u00b7 leaching</td><td class=\"val\">10 weeks active</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Crew Beta Lead</td><td>Soil amendment application \u00b7 incorporation</td><td class=\"val\">8 weeks active</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Crew Gamma Lead</td><td>Planting operations \u00b7 seedling handling \u00b7 GPS logging</td><td class=\"val\">12 weeks active</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Crew Delta Lead</td><td>Field monitoring \u00b7 sampling \u00b7 data upload to DROS</td><td class=\"val\">Mo 8\u201324 (ongoing)</td><td class=\"center val\">1.0</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 02. CREWS -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"crews\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--blue-lt);color:var(--blue)\">&#x1F477;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 02</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Crew Composition</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"crew-grid\">\n    <div class=\"crew-card alpha\">\n      <div class=\"crew-header\"><span class=\"crew-name\">Crew Alpha</span><span class=\"crew-size\">6 personnel</span></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-mission\"><strong>Mission:</strong> Site preparation, earthworks, salinity knockdown. Heavy machinery operations.</div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>Period</span><strong>Wk 1\u201310</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Crew lead</span><strong>Sr. operator</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Surveyor</span><strong>GPS staking</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>2\u00d7 Machine operators</span><strong>Ripper \u00b7 spreader</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>2\u00d7 Ground crew</span><strong>Manual labor</strong></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"crew-card beta\">\n      <div class=\"crew-header\"><span class=\"crew-name\">Crew Beta</span><span class=\"crew-size\">5 personnel</span></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-mission\"><strong>Mission:</strong> Soil amendment application, biochar/compost spreading, biological inoculation.</div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>Period</span><strong>Wk 9\u201316</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Crew lead</span><strong>Application supervisor</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Spreader operator</span><strong>Tractor-mounted</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>2\u00d7 Application crew</span><strong>Hand spread + spray</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Quality checker</span><strong>Dose verification</strong></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"crew-card gamma\">\n      <div class=\"crew-header\"><span class=\"crew-name\">Crew Gamma</span><span class=\"crew-size\">10 personnel</span></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-mission\"><strong>Mission:</strong> Planting operations. Largest crew. Cool-season deployment. Per-tree GPS logging.</div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>Period</span><strong>Wk 20\u201332</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Crew lead</span><strong>Planting supervisor</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 GPS operator</span><strong>Tree-by-tree logging</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>2\u00d7 Pit prep crew</span><strong>50\u00d750\u00d750 cm pits</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>6\u00d7 Planting crew</span><strong>~200 trees/day each</strong></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"crew-card delta\">\n      <div class=\"crew-header\"><span class=\"crew-name\">Crew Delta</span><span class=\"crew-size\">3 personnel</span></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-mission\"><strong>Mission:</strong> Long-term monitoring, sample collection, data upload, maintenance flushes.</div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>Period</span><strong>Mo 8\u201324</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Field tech lead</span><strong>Sampling + lab liaison</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Survey assistant</span><strong>NDVI ground truth</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>1\u00d7 Irrigation tech</span><strong>System maintenance</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"crew-stat\"><span>Frequency</span><strong>Weekly site visits</strong></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 03. SCHEDULE -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"schedule\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--blue-lt);color:var(--blue)\">&#x1F4C5;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 03</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Weekly Shift Schedule</h2></div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"section-desc\">Standard working week is Sunday\u2013Thursday with Saturday optional for catch-up. Friday is rest day per KSA labour law. Morning shifts run 0500\u20131100 (5\u00b0C cooler), afternoon shifts 1500\u20131900 when LST drops below 32\u00b0C.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\"><span class=\"sub-num\">3.1</span> Typical week \u2014 Phase 2 (week 10)</div>\n  <div class=\"week-grid\">\n    <div class=\"wg-header\">\n      <div class=\"wg-day\">Crew</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Sun</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Mon</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Tue</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Wed</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Thu</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Fri</div><div class=\"wg-day\">Sat</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"wg-row\">\n      <div class=\"wg-crew\"><span style=\"width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--red);flex-shrink:0\"></span>Crew Alpha</div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--red)\">AM</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--red)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--red)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--red)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--red)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">OFF</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:#d8b88a\">OPT</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"wg-row\">\n      <div class=\"wg-crew\"><span style=\"width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--amber);flex-shrink:0\"></span>Crew Beta</div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--amber)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--amber)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--amber)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--amber)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--amber)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">OFF</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:#d8b88a\">OPT</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"wg-row\">\n      <div class=\"wg-crew\"><span style=\"width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);flex-shrink:0\"></span>Crew Gamma</div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"wg-row\">\n      <div class=\"wg-crew\"><span style=\"width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--blue);flex-shrink:0\"></span>Crew Delta</div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--blue)\">AM</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--blue)\">AM</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">OFF</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">\u2014</div></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"wg-row\">\n      <div class=\"wg-crew\"><span style=\"width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--ink);flex-shrink:0\"></span>Ops Manager</div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--ink)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--ink)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--ink)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--ink)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--ink)\">FULL</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:var(--dim)\">OFF</div></div>\n      <div class=\"wg-cell\"><div class=\"wg-shift\" style=\"background:#888\">ON-CALL</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub-title\"><span class=\"sub-num\">3.2</span> Daily shift hours</div>\n  <table class=\"dtable\">\n    <thead><tr><th>Shift</th><th>Hours</th><th>Conditions</th><th>Applies to</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Morning (cool)</td><td class=\"val\">05:00 \u2013 11:00</td><td>LST &lt; 32\u00b0C \u00b7 primary work window</td><td>All physical crews</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-crit\"><td class=\"param\">Midday (rest)</td><td class=\"val\">11:00 \u2013 15:00</td><td>LST 32\u201348\u00b0C \u00b7 MANDATORY rest period</td><td>HSE rule \u00b7 no exceptions</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Afternoon (resume)</td><td class=\"val\">15:00 \u2013 19:00</td><td>LST falls below 32\u00b0C \u00b7 light tasks only</td><td>Beta, Gamma crews</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-warn\"><td class=\"param\">Cool season variant</td><td class=\"val\">06:00 \u2013 14:00</td><td>October\u2013March \u00b7 single shift</td><td>All crews</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 04. MACHINERY -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"machinery\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--amber-lt);color:var(--amber)\">&#x1F69C;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 04</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Machinery &amp; Equipment Deployment</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <table class=\"dtable\">\n    <thead><tr><th>Equipment</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Period</th><th>Source</th><th class=\"center\">Qty</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Subsoil ripper (1.5 m tine)</td><td>Deep ripping to 60 cm</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 3\u20135</td><td>Rental \u00b7 Al-Jazirah Ag</td><td class=\"center val\">1</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Tractor 90+ HP (4WD)</td><td>Ripper, spreader, rotovator tow</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 1\u201314</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">2</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Spreader truck (capacity 5 t)</td><td>Gypsum, compost, biochar broadcast</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 4\u201314</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">1</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Rotovator (3 m width)</td><td>Amendment incorporation to 25\u201330 cm</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 10\u201311</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">1</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Drilling rig (rotary)</td><td>Borehole to 40 m + planting pit auger</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 2\u20133, 18\u201322</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">1</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Excavator (3 t mini)</td><td>Swales, retention basins, access tracks</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 3\u20136</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">1</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Water bowser (10,000 L)</td><td>Leaching flush, irrigation startup</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 5\u20138</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">2</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Spray rig (mounted)</td><td>Cyanobacteria, PGPR, micronutrient foliar</td><td class=\"val\">Wk 11\u201322</td><td>Rental</td><td class=\"center val\">1</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Field testing kit</td><td>Hanna HI98195 pH/EC \u00b7 Munsell \u00b7 GPS</td><td class=\"val\">All phases</td><td>Owned</td><td class=\"center val\">2</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Vehicles (4WD pickup)</td><td>Crew transport, sample logistics</td><td class=\"val\">24 months</td><td>Owned/leased</td><td class=\"center val\">2</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 SOPs \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n\n<!-- 05. SOP - GYPSUM -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-gypsum\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 05</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 01 \u00b7 Gypsum Application</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-01 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Gypsum broadcast &amp; leaching flush</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-crit\">CRITICAL</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Alpha</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Purpose</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Displace exchangeable sodium from soil colloids using calcium from gypsum, then flush sodium below root zone with controlled irrigation.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Materials</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Gypsum (CaSO&#8324;&middot;2H&#8322;O) ag-grade &gt;85% purity, ground &lt;2mm <span class=\"dose\">5 t/ha</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Tools required</div>\n        <div class=\"tool-list\"><span class=\"tool-chip\">Spreader truck</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Tractor</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Rotovator</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Water bowser</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">pH/EC meter</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Dust masks</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Pre-check:</strong> Verify deep rip completed to 60 cm. Confirm no rain forecast for 7 days. Wind speed &lt;20 km/h.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Calibrate spreader:</strong> Set discharge rate to 500 kg per 100 m run at 8 km/h. Test on tarp, weigh, adjust.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Broadcast pattern:</strong> Parallel runs with 1 m overlap. Cover full 100 ha. Monitor for missed strips with GPS tracker.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Incorporate within 24 hours:</strong> Rotovate to 30 cm depth. Two passes perpendicular to each other for even distribution.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Leaching flush:</strong> Apply <span class=\"dose\">150\u2013200 mm</span> irrigation. Water bowser delivery if drip not yet operational. Allow 72 hrs drainage.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">06</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Verification (Gate 1):</strong> Sample 5 points at 0\u201330 cm depth. Field test EC. Lab confirm SAR. <strong>Both must pass</strong> before proceeding.</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Safety</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Dust masks during broadcast. No spreading in winds &gt;20 km/h. Avoid skin contact with concentrated gypsum dust \u2014 rinse immediately.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Quality criteria</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\"><strong>Pass:</strong> EC &lt;3.0 dS/m and SAR &lt;13 at all 5 sample points after flush. <strong>Fail:</strong> Apply additional 2 t/ha gypsum + repeat flush.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 06. SOP - DEEP RIP -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-rip\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 06</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 02 \u00b7 Deep Ripping</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-02 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Subsoil ripping to break compaction layer</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-warn\">REQUIRED</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Alpha</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Purpose</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Break the compacted subsoil layer (bulk density 1.62 g/cm&#179;) to allow root penetration and improve infiltration before amendment application.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Tools required</div>\n        <div class=\"tool-list\"><span class=\"tool-chip\">Subsoil ripper \u00b7 1.5m tine</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Tractor 90+ HP 4WD</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">GPS tracker</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Depth check rod</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Set tine depth:</strong> 60 cm below surface. Verify with calibration stick before starting.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Row spacing:</strong> <span class=\"dose\">1.0\u20131.5 m</span> between rip lines. Mark first row with GPS, drive parallel.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Operating speed:</strong> 6\u20138 km/h. Slower in hard ground. Watch for tine deflection \u2014 indicates rock or hardpan.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Coverage check:</strong> After every 5 ha, verify depth at 3 points using rod insertion test. Should reach 55+ cm freely.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Cross-ripping (optional):</strong> If subsoil very hard (clay layer), perform second pass at 90\u00b0 to first.</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Quality criteria</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Bulk density retest at 30 cm and 60 cm must drop below 1.5 g/cm&#179;. If not, increase row density to 0.8 m spacing.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 07. SOP - BIOCHAR -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-biochar\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 07</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 03 \u00b7 Biochar &amp; Compost Application</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-03 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Biochar + compost + sulfur incorporation</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-crit\">CRITICAL</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Beta</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Purpose</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Increase WHC from 11% to &gt;20%, raise organic matter from 0.35% to &gt;2%, and begin pH correction in a single combined application pass.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Materials &amp; rates</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Biochar <span class=\"dose\">15 t/ha</span> \u00b7 Compost <span class=\"dose\">20 t/ha</span> \u00b7 Elemental sulfur <span class=\"dose\">2.5 t/ha</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Tools required</div>\n        <div class=\"tool-list\"><span class=\"tool-chip\">Spreader truck</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Tractor</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Rotovator</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Water bowser (dust suppression)</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Dust masks N95</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Pre-wet biochar:</strong> Spray biochar piles with water 12 hrs before spreading. Reduces UV degradation and prevents windborne loss.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Layered spread:</strong> First pass = sulfur 2.5 t/ha. Second pass = compost 20 t/ha. Third pass = biochar 15 t/ha. Layered approach prevents tractor wheel sinking.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Incorporate immediately:</strong> Rotovate to 25\u201330 cm depth <strong>within 24 hours</strong> of biochar spread. UV degrades surface biochar &mdash; do not delay.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Verify mixing:</strong> Dig 5 test pits at 30 cm depth. Should see uniform brown-black soil mix with no concentrated biochar bands.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Light irrigation:</strong> Apply 20\u201330 mm via drip to settle and activate. Begin Thiobacillus sulfur oxidation cycle.</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Safety</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">N95 dust masks mandatory during biochar handling. Avoid open flames near biochar dust (combustible). No spreading in winds &gt;15 km/h.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 08. SOP - CYANO SPRAY -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-spray\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 08</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 04 \u00b7 Cyanobacteria Spray Inoculation</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-04 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Nostoc biocrust spray</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-info\">SCHEDULED</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Beta</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Purpose</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Establish biological soil crust to stabilize surface, reduce wind erosion, and provide nitrogen fixation through <em>Nostoc</em> cyanobacteria.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Materials</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\"><em>Nostoc</em> spp. dried biomass <span class=\"dose\">2\u20135 kg/ha</span> in 200 L water + 0.1% molasses (food source for activation)</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Tools required</div>\n        <div class=\"tool-list\"><span class=\"tool-chip\">Spray rig (mounted)</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Mixing tank 500 L</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Whisk / agitator</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Spray nozzles fine mist</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Timing:</strong> Apply only in early morning (05:00\u201307:30). Soil temp must be &lt;30\u00b0C. Forecast: no wind, no rain for 48 hrs.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Mix solution:</strong> Dissolve molasses in warm water first. Add Nostoc biomass slowly while stirring. Use within 4 hours of mixing.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Spray application:</strong> Fine mist setting (not stream). Walk pace 1 m/sec. Even coverage at 200 L per ha.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Light moistening:</strong> If forecast dry &gt;5 days, follow with light drip (5 mm) on day 2 to prevent dessication.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Repeat application:</strong> Weekly for 4 applications. Spot-check for visible green-brown crust formation by week 6\u20138.</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Quality criteria</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Visible biocrust forming on &gt;30% of treated area by week 8. Chlorophyll-a test &gt;2 \u00b5g/cm&#178; on surface scrape.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 09. SOP - PLANTING -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-plant\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 09</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 05 \u00b7 Tree Planting</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-05 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Standard tree planting with AMF + WaterLock</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-crit\">CRITICAL</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Gamma</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Purpose</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Plant a seedling with mycorrhizal inoculant, water-retention hydrogel, and shade shelter for maximum first-year survival in arid saline soil.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Materials per tree</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">1\u00d7 seedling \u00b7 AMF inoculant <span class=\"dose\">10\u201315 g</span> \u00b7 WaterLock KPA <span class=\"dose\">5\u201310 g</span> \u00b7 Shade shelter \u00b7 1\u00d7 drip emitter</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Tools required</div>\n        <div class=\"tool-list\"><span class=\"tool-chip\">Auger / shovel</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Measuring stick (50 cm)</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">GPS unit</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Water can / bowser</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Cooler (AMF storage 4\u201315\u00b0C)</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Excavate pit:</strong> 50 cm diameter \u00d7 50 cm deep. Verify with measuring stick.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Backfill base:</strong> Add 10 cm of amended soil (compost+biochar mix) at bottom. Sprinkle WaterLock 5\u201310 g at this layer.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Place AMF:</strong> Sprinkle <span class=\"dose\">10\u201315 g granular AMF</span> at 5\u201310 cm below where root ball will sit. Direct root contact is critical.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Position seedling:</strong> Remove from nursery pot gently. Place root ball directly on AMF layer. Crown at original soil line.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Backfill &amp; firm:</strong> Fill with amended soil. Firm gently around root ball. Do not compact heavily.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">06</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Form micro-basin:</strong> Build 15 cm ring around tree to capture water. Diameter 60 cm.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">07</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>First watering:</strong> 10 L per tree using watering can to settle backfill. Note any subsidence.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">08</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Install shade shelter:</strong> 50% shade cloth on 3 bamboo stakes. Angle south to block midday sun.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">09</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Connect drip emitter:</strong> Position 2 L/hr emitter at root ball edge, 5 cm from trunk.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">10</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>GPS log:</strong> Record coordinate, species, planting date, planter ID. Upload to DROS within 24 hrs.</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Productivity target</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">~200 trees per planter per day with full QA procedure followed. Crew of 6 planters = 1,200 trees/day = 100 ha completion in 21 working days.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 10. SOP - IRRIGATION -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-irrigate\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 10</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 06 \u00b7 Irrigation Operation</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-06 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Daily irrigation cycle with leaching fraction</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-warn\">ONGOING</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Delta</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Pre-start check:</strong> Visual inspection of mainline pressure (target 1.5\u20132.0 bar). Confirm tank levels &gt;50%. Check filter pressure differential &lt;0.5 bar.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Zone activation:</strong> Open zone valves sequentially (Z1 \u2192 Z4). Allow 5 min for pressure stabilization.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Run duration:</strong> Establishment phase 45 min daily. Early growth 60 min every 2 days. See full schedule.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Leaching fraction:</strong> Add 25% extra duration every 5th cycle to push salts below root zone. Critical for groundwater EC 2.8.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Flow check:</strong> Walk 3 random emitters during run. Verify ~2 L/hr discharge. Replace clogged emitters immediately.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">06</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Shutdown:</strong> Close zones reverse order. Drain mainline to prevent stagnant water. Record run-time and any issues.</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Weekly maintenance</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Backflush filters \u00b7 clean tank screens \u00b7 check pump amperage draw \u00b7 flush distal end of each lateral \u00b7 injection point cleanup.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 11. SOP - SAMPLING -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"sop-sample\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--green-lt);color:var(--green)\">&#x1F4D6;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 11</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">SOP 07 \u00b7 Soil Sample Collection</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sop-card\">\n    <div class=\"sop-header\">\n      <div><div class=\"sop-id\">SOP-DROS-07 \u00b7 REV 1</div><div class=\"sop-title\">Stratified composite sampling for lab analysis</div></div>\n      <div class=\"sop-meta\"><span class=\"st st-warn\">SCHEDULED</span><span class=\"st st-info\">Crew Delta + Soil Sci.</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sop-body\">\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Purpose</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">Collect representative soil samples for laboratory analysis to verify gate conditions, monitor amendment efficacy, and track SOC accumulation for carbon credits.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Tools required</div>\n        <div class=\"tool-list\"><span class=\"tool-chip\">Stainless steel auger</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Depth ruler</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Sterile 250mL bags</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Falcon tubes (microbial)</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Cooler + ice packs</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">GPS unit</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Permanent marker</span><span class=\"tool-chip\">Nitrile gloves</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Procedure</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">01</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>GPS navigate</strong> to pre-marked sample point. Record exact coordinates.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">02</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Composite sampling:</strong> Take 15\u201320 sub-samples in a 25 m radius \"W\" pattern around the GPS point. Combine in bucket.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">03</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Depth stratification:</strong> Separate samples by depth: 0\u201310 cm \u00b7 10\u201330 cm \u00b7 30\u201360 cm. Clean auger between depths.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">04</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Microbial sub-sample (priority):</strong> <strong>Before</strong> mixing composite, take 100 g into sterile Falcon tube. Place on ice immediately.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">05</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Mix composite:</strong> Thoroughly mix remaining material. Quarter and reduce to ~500 g final sample. Place in labeled bag.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">06</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Label:</strong> Sample ID format <code>P##-A/B/C</code> (point number + depth code). Date \u00b7 time \u00b7 collector initials.</span></div>\n        <div class=\"sop-step\"><span class=\"sop-step-num\">07</span><span class=\"sop-step-text\"><strong>Chain of custody:</strong> Complete CoC form on transfer to courier. Microbial samples to lab within 24\u201348 hrs (cold chain).</span></div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sop-section\">\n        <div class=\"sop-label\">Critical rules</div>\n        <div class=\"sop-content\"><strong>Microbial samples must reach lab within 48 hrs.</strong> Do not freeze unless lab specifies. Stainless steel auger only (galvanized contaminates with zinc).</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \u2550\u2550\u2550 TACTICAL PLAN \u2550\u2550\u2550 -->\n\n<!-- 12. ZONE MAP -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"zones\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red)\">&#x1F5FA;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 12</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Site Zone Map</h2></div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"section-desc\">The 100-hectare parcel is divided into four operational zones based on satellite-derived NDVI and BSI clustering. Each zone has a distinct work sequence, crew assignment, and amendment intensity.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"zone-map\">\n    <div class=\"zone-map-header\">\n      <span class=\"zone-map-title\">Operational zones \u2014 work sequence A \u2192 B \u2192 C \u2192 D</span>\n      <span class=\"st st-crit\">4 zones</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zone-map-body\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 700 340\" class=\"zone-map-svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid slice\">\n        <defs>\n          <pattern id=\"bg-pattern\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\"><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"4\" r=\"0.4\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.04)\"/></pattern>\n        </defs>\n        <rect width=\"700\" height=\"340\" fill=\"#1a2418\"/>\n        <rect width=\"700\" height=\"340\" fill=\"url(#bg-pattern)\"/>\n\n        <!-- Topo contours -->\n        <g stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,.05)\" stroke-width=\"0.8\" fill=\"none\">\n          <path d=\"M0 80 Q200 70 400 80 Q600 90 700 80\"/>\n          <path d=\"M0 160 Q200 145 400 160 Q600 175 700 160\"/>\n          <path d=\"M0 240 Q200 225 400 240 Q600 255 700 240\"/>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Zone A (62%) \u2014 critical -->\n        <path d=\"M50 50 L320 50 L350 90 L370 180 L340 240 L100 250 L50 200Z\" fill=\"rgba(176,58,46,.25)\" stroke=\"#E05C3A\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 2\"/>\n        <text x=\"180\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#ff8a7a\" font-family=\"Source Serif 4\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"700\">ZONE A</text>\n        <text x=\"180\" y=\"153\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,180,170,.6)\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" text-anchor=\"middle\">CRITICAL \u00b7 62 ha</text>\n        <text x=\"180\" y=\"168\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,180,170,.5)\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Crew Alpha \u2192 Beta \u2192 Gamma</text>\n\n        <!-- Zone B (24%) -->\n        <path d=\"M350 60 L580 70 L600 150 L560 220 L370 230 L340 130Z\" fill=\"rgba(184,121,26,.25)\" stroke=\"#E5A52F\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 2\"/>\n        <text x=\"475\" y=\"135\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#f0b860\" font-family=\"Source Serif 4\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"700\">ZONE B</text>\n        <text x=\"475\" y=\"153\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(240,200,140,.6)\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" text-anchor=\"middle\">HIGH \u00b7 24 ha</text>\n        <text x=\"475\" y=\"168\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(240,200,140,.5)\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Crew Alpha (light) \u2192 Gamma</text>\n\n        <!-- Zone C (10%) -->\n        <path d=\"M580 70 L660 80 L670 160 L650 210 L590 190 L575 140Z\" fill=\"rgba(138,170,74,.25)\" stroke=\"#a0c060\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 2\"/>\n        <text x=\"620\" y=\"130\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#bdd680\" font-family=\"Source Serif 4\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">ZONE C</text>\n        <text x=\"620\" y=\"145\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(189,214,128,.5)\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" text-anchor=\"middle\">10 ha</text>\n\n        <!-- Zone D (4%) - remnant -->\n        <ellipse cx=\"120\" cy=\"100\" rx=\"42\" ry=\"32\" fill=\"rgba(42,125,79,.3)\" stroke=\"#5aab7a\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#7bc594\" font-family=\"Source Serif 4\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-weight=\"600\">ZONE D</text>\n        <text x=\"120\" y=\"118\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(123,197,148,.6)\" font-family=\"JetBrains Mono\" text-anchor=\"middle\">4 ha \u00b7 protect</text>\n\n        <!-- Borehole locations -->\n        <circle cx=\"220\" cy=\"180\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#3a8fd4\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <text x=\"234\" y=\"183\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.7)\" font-family=\"Inter\">Borehole 1</text>\n        <circle cx=\"480\" cy=\"180\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#3a8fd4\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/>\n        <text x=\"494\" y=\"183\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.7)\" font-family=\"Inter\">Borehole 2 (backup)</text>\n\n        <!-- Storage tanks -->\n        <rect x=\"208\" y=\"200\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#5aab7a\"/>\n        <rect x=\"220\" y=\"200\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#5aab7a\"/>\n        <rect x=\"232\" y=\"200\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" fill=\"#5aab7a\"/>\n        <text x=\"244\" y=\"208\" font-size=\"7\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.5)\" font-family=\"Inter\">Tanks \u00d73</text>\n\n        <!-- Retention basins -->\n        <ellipse cx=\"100\" cy=\"290\" rx=\"14\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(58,143,212,.4)\" stroke=\"#3a8fd4\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <ellipse cx=\"350\" cy=\"290\" rx=\"14\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(58,143,212,.4)\" stroke=\"#3a8fd4\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <ellipse cx=\"600\" cy=\"280\" rx=\"14\" ry=\"6\" fill=\"rgba(58,143,212,.4)\" stroke=\"#3a8fd4\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n        <text x=\"350\" y=\"312\" font-size=\"7\" fill=\"rgba(58,143,212,.7)\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\">Retention basins \u00d73</text>\n\n        <!-- Access track -->\n        <path d=\"M30 320 Q200 318 400 325 Q600 332 690 320\" stroke=\"rgba(201,132,26,.4)\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"6 3\"/>\n        <text x=\"40\" y=\"316\" font-size=\"7\" fill=\"rgba(201,132,26,.5)\" font-family=\"Inter\">Access track</text>\n\n        <!-- Compass -->\n        <g transform=\"translate(660,40)\">\n          <circle r=\"12\" fill=\"rgba(15,28,19,.7)\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,.2)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n          <text x=\"0\" y=\"-12\" font-size=\"7\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.7)\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-family=\"Inter\" font-weight=\"700\">N</text>\n          <path d=\"M0 -8L2 0L0 4L-2 0Z\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.8)\"/>\n        </g>\n\n        <!-- Scale -->\n        <g transform=\"translate(30,30)\">\n          <rect width=\"60\" height=\"2\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.4)\" rx=\"1\"/>\n          <text x=\"0\" y=\"14\" font-size=\"7\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.4)\" font-family=\"Inter\">0</text>\n          <text x=\"50\" y=\"14\" font-size=\"7\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,.4)\" font-family=\"Inter\">500 m</text>\n        </g>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 13. ZONE WORK PLANS -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"zone-plans\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red)\">&#x1F4CB;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 13</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Zone-by-Zone Work Plans</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"zone-grid\">\n    <div class=\"zone-card zone-a\">\n      <div class=\"zone-name\">Zone A \u2014 Critical Degradation</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-area\">62 ha \u00b7 62% of total area \u00b7 NDVI 0.055 \u00b7 BSI 0.92</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Priority</span><strong style=\"color:var(--red)\">IMMEDIATE</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Treatment</span><strong>Full protocol</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Gypsum dose</span><strong>5 t/ha (full)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Biochar dose</span><strong>15 t/ha (full)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Compost dose</span><strong>20 t/ha (full)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Tree density</span><strong>250/ha (~15,500)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Field samples</span><strong>8\u201310 points</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Crew sequence</span><strong>Alpha \u2192 Beta \u2192 Gamma</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Duration</span><strong>Weeks 1\u201332</strong></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zone-card zone-b\">\n      <div class=\"zone-name\">Zone B \u2014 High Degradation</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-area\">24 ha \u00b7 24% of total area \u00b7 NDVI 0.085 \u00b7 BSI 0.78</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Priority</span><strong style=\"color:var(--amber)\">HIGH</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Treatment</span><strong>Standard protocol</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Gypsum dose</span><strong>4 t/ha (reduced)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Biochar dose</span><strong>12 t/ha (reduced)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Compost dose</span><strong>20 t/ha (full)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Tree density</span><strong>250/ha (~6,000)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Field samples</span><strong>5\u20136 points</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Crew sequence</span><strong>Alpha (light) \u2192 Gamma</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Duration</span><strong>Weeks 5\u201328</strong></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zone-card zone-c\">\n      <div class=\"zone-name\">Zone C \u2014 Moderate (Wadi Edge)</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-area\">10 ha \u00b7 10% of total area \u00b7 NDVI 0.140 \u00b7 BSI 0.55</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Priority</span><strong style=\"color:#a0c060\">MODERATE</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Treatment</span><strong>Light protocol</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Gypsum dose</span><strong>2 t/ha (spot)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Biochar dose</span><strong>8 t/ha</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Compost dose</span><strong>15 t/ha</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Tree density</span><strong>180/ha (~1,800)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Field samples</span><strong>3\u20134 points</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Crew sequence</span><strong>Gamma direct</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Duration</span><strong>Weeks 14\u201328</strong></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"zone-card zone-d\">\n      <div class=\"zone-name\">Zone D \u2014 Remnant Vegetation</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-area\">4 ha \u00b7 4% of total area \u00b7 NDVI 0.280 \u00b7 BSI 0.30</div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Priority</span><strong style=\"color:var(--green)\">PROTECT</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Treatment</span><strong>Minimal \u2014 protect</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Gypsum dose</span><strong>None</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Biochar dose</span><strong>None</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Compost dose</span><strong>None (topdress only)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Tree density</span><strong>Infill 80/ha (~320)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Field samples</span><strong>2\u20133 points</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Crew sequence</span><strong>Gamma (careful)</strong></div>\n      <div class=\"zone-row\"><span>Duration</span><strong>Weeks 20\u201324</strong></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 14. DEPENDENCIES -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"dependencies\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--purple-lt);color:var(--purple)\">&#x1F517;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 14</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Task Dependencies &amp; Critical Path</h2></div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"section-desc\">The rehabilitation has a strict critical path. Six tasks must be completed sequentially before planting \u2014 any delay cascades. The first 10 weeks (site prep + amendment) is the critical path. Tasks marked BLOCKER halt downstream work if delayed.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"dep-block\">\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T01</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Site fencing &amp; survey</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Alpha \u00b7 No predecessor</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker no\">No blocker</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">2 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T02</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Borehole drilling + pump test</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Alpha \u00b7 After T01</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">BLOCKER for all irrigation</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">2 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T03</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Deep ripping to 60 cm</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Alpha \u00b7 Parallel to T02</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">BLOCKER for amendments</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">3 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T04</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Swales + retention basins</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Alpha \u00b7 Parallel to T03</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker no\">Soft blocker</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">2 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T05</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Gypsum + leaching flush</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Alpha \u00b7 After T02 + T03</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">BLOCKER \u00b7 Gate 1</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">3 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T06</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">EC retest (Gate 1)</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Soil Scientist \u00b7 After T05</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">HARD GATE</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">1 week</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T07</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Biochar + compost + sulfur</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Beta \u00b7 After T06 pass</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">BLOCKER for planting</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">2 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T08</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Cyanobacteria spray \u00d74</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Beta \u00b7 Parallel</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker no\">No blocker</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">4 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T09</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">pH retest (Gate 2)</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Soil Scientist \u00b7 After T07</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">HARD GATE</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">1 week</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T10</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">NPK + AMF inoculation</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Beta \u00b7 After T09 pass</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">BLOCKER for planting</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">2 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T11</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Pit excavation (25K pits)</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Gamma \u00b7 After T10</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker no\">No blocker</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">3 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dep-row\">\n      <div class=\"dep-id\">T12</div>\n      <div><div class=\"dep-name\">Tree planting + GPS log</div><div class=\"dep-meta\">Crew Gamma \u00b7 After T11</div></div>\n      <div><span class=\"dep-blocker\">CRITICAL PATH</span></div>\n      <div class=\"dep-duration\">12 weeks</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"gate\"><div class=\"gate-icon\">!</div><div class=\"gate-body\"><strong>Critical path total: 33 weeks</strong> (T01 \u2192 T12). Any delay before planting cannot be recovered in the cool season. If Gate 1 fails at T06, the entire planting window slips by minimum 4 weeks.</div></div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- 15. CONTINGENCY -->\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"contingency\">\n  <div class=\"section-bar\">\n    <div class=\"section-icon\" style=\"background:var(--red-lt);color:var(--red)\">&#x1F6A8;</div>\n    <div><div class=\"section-num\">Section 15</div><h2 class=\"section-title\">Contingency Procedures</h2></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <table class=\"dtable\">\n    <thead><tr><th>Scenario</th><th>Trigger</th><th>Response action</th><th class=\"center\">Authority</th></tr></thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"row-crit\"><td class=\"param\">Gate 1 failure</td><td>EC &gt;3.0 after flush</td><td>+2 t/ha gypsum \u00b7 repeat flush \u00b7 +1 week delay</td><td class=\"center val\">Soil Sci.</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-crit\"><td class=\"param\">Gate 2 failure</td><td>pH &gt;7.8 at wk 16</td><td>+1 t/ha sulfur \u00b7 wait 4 wk \u00b7 retest</td><td class=\"center val\">Soil Sci.</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-crit\"><td class=\"param\">Groundwater fail</td><td>Yield &lt;3 m\u00b3/hr</td><td>Drill second borehole \u00b7 negotiate municipal water \u00b7 4 week delay</td><td class=\"center val\">Project Lead</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-warn\"><td class=\"param\">Heat wave (LST &gt;45\u00b0C)</td><td>Forecast 3+ days</td><td>Suspend physical work \u00b7 maintain irrigation \u00b7 HSE briefing</td><td class=\"center val\">HSE Officer</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-warn\"><td class=\"param\">Dust storm</td><td>Visibility &lt;200 m</td><td>Crew stand-down \u00b7 secure equipment \u00b7 spreading ops cancelled</td><td class=\"center val\">Ops Manager</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-warn\"><td class=\"param\">Biochar shipment delay</td><td>&gt;2 weeks late</td><td>Switch to UAE distributor (premium price) \u00b7 activate backup PO</td><td class=\"center val\">Project Lead</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-warn\"><td class=\"param\">Survival &lt;50% at mo 6</td><td>Field audit result</td><td>Diagnose root zone \u00b7 full replant in next cool season \u00b7 adjust irrigation</td><td class=\"center val\">Soil Sci.</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Equipment breakdown</td><td>&gt;48 hr downtime</td><td>Switch to backup rental \u00b7 contact secondary supplier \u00b7 log delay</td><td class=\"center val\">Ops Manager</td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"row-info\"><td class=\"param\">Crew shortage</td><td>&gt;20% absentee</td><td>Engage day labor from local pool \u00b7 pause non-critical tasks</td><td class=\"center val\">Ops Manager</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n\n  <div class=\"gate warn\"><div class=\"gate-icon\">!</div><div class=\"gate-body\"><strong>Communication chain:</strong> All contingency activations must be logged in DROS within 4 hours. Project Lead notification within 24 hours. Client briefing within 72 hours for any &gt;1 week schedule impact.</div></div>\n\n  <div class=\"disclaimer\">\n    <p>This field execution plan is the operational playbook for implementation of DROS-RPL-2026-001. All standard operating procedures must be followed in sequence. Gate conditions are non-negotiable checkpoints \u2014 proceeding without meeting gate criteria voids the projected outcomes of the rehabilitation plan and may invalidate carbon credit chain of custody. Daily field logs (DROS-FEX-2026-001) must be completed alongside this plan.</p>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:12px\"><strong>Document:</strong> DROS-FEP-2026-001 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <strong>Version:</strong> 1.0 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <strong>Linked:</strong> RPL-2026-001 + FEX-2026-001 &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <strong>Print for site office wall display</strong></p>\n  </div>\n</div>"

